information: The company BAUUNTERNEHMUNG WILHELM WEIER GMBH & CO. KG, is a Manufacturer/ Producer, founded in 1967, which operates in the Indoor and greenhouse plants, floristry industry. It also operates in the Nurseries, Textile plants, Raw materials for construction and public works, and Structural work industries. It is based in Duisburg, Germany.
